task.summary: Day 1 - Implemented basic static Window class using GLFW as well as a preliminary game loop and timing system in the MainComponent class.
Day 2 - Converted to LWJGL 2.9.3 for simpler window creation and input, and added input class.
Day 4 - Created static utility classes and Mesh and Vertex classes, prepared for rendering.
Day 4 Pt. 2 - Added shader class and basic shaders.
Day 4 Pt. 3 - Fixed a stupid error in Mesh class -.-
Day 5 - Added support for uniform variables.
Day 6 - Added Transform class and helper methods in Matrix4f class.
Day 7 Pt. 1 - Added support for index buffer objects in preparation for loading obj files.
Day 7 Pt. 2 - Buggy, temporary obj loader.
Day 7 Pt. 3 - Cleanup, fixed a bug with IBO's in Mesh class.
Day 8 - Improved the crappy OBJ loader and added a simple 3D Camera class.
